  "title": "Regional Sales Manager (Semiconductor Equipment)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Drive regional sales of semiconductor manufacturing equipment (full systems, not components/modules) across Southeast Asia and assigned territories.</li>\n  <li>Manage strategic accounts including foundries, IDMs, OSATs, and OEMs; identify and secure new business opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with engineering and product teams to deliver tailored equipment solutions and lead contract negotiations to close deals.</li>\n  <li>Track market trends, customer roadmaps, and competitor activity; maintain accurate forecasts, CRM updates, and represent the company at industry events.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering or Marketing.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of <strong>equipment sales </strong>experience in the <strong>semiconductor manufacturing industry</strong>, preferably in <strong>back-end processes</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Good understanding of fab and OSAT workflows, qualification protocols, and CapEx planning cycles.</li>\n  <li>Strong customer connections and ability to work independently.</li>\n  <li>Able to travel moderately across Southeast Asia and assigned regions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R21100996</p>",
